Crystals dont have polarity.  One thing though is that they are designed for specific load capacitances.  I'd be suprised if that were the actual issue though.  But its conceivable that you had a good crystal at the right frequency, but wrong system capacitance for the first crystal.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4832">infiniteneslives</a> — Sun Jun 10, 2012 1:55 am</p><hr />
